1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 12=
(My Man)

3
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,599
I heard what happened today.

4
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:27,480
It was all about the resort.

5
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:28,359
Maybe

6
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,159
you should sell the resort,

7
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,319
stay home,

8
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:34,239
and just be Mrs. He.

9
00:01:37,079 --> 00:01:38,719
What is the benefit of being Mrs. He?

10
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,640
I'm doing this for your own good.

11
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:43,879
See,

12
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:45,519
you can't even figure it out yourself.

13
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,799
I have been Mrs. He for so long.

14
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,560
Have you ever respected me

15
00:01:49,719 --> 00:01:50,719
or cared about me?

16
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,959
You don't care about me at all.

17
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:57,200
You only care about the resort.

18
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,400
Three times the market price.

19
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:07,439
That is already my best offer.

20
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:10,560
I'm not selling it.

21
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:14,280
Why are you so stubborn
about this rundown resort?

22
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:16,879
Then why is Shengda so determined
to buy it?

23
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:20,000
What are you planning to do with it?

24
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,599
Why would you ask that?

25
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:25,599
Nothing.

26
00:02:26,319 --> 00:02:26,960
Just curious.

27
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:30,680
So I would like you to enlighten me,
Mr. He.

28
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,520
I'm taking over the resort

29
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:41,960
because I can unlock

30
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,199
greater value from this land.

31
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:43,879
Besides,

32
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,520
it is for your own good.

33
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,000
Thank you, Mr. He.

34
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:48,319
But no need.

35
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,159
I can handle it myself.

36
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,800
And

37
00:02:52,319 --> 00:02:53,240
there are things

38
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,639
that money just can't buy.

39
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:57,800
I don't understand.

40
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,039
As a businessman,

41
00:02:59,199 --> 00:03:00,080
if not money,

42
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,319
then what else is there?

43
00:03:04,879 --> 00:03:07,280
For example, the last clean water zone.

44
00:03:08,439 --> 00:03:09,400
Money cannot buy it.

45
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,560
Misplaced mercy.

46
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,120
Fine.

47
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:18,439
When this resort goes bankrupt,

48
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,120
you will be begging me to buy it.

49
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,080
I'm afraid

50
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,240
that day will not come.

51
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:54,840
Beautiful.

52
00:04:05,439 --> 00:04:05,960
Boss.

53
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,919
You bunch of useless idiots!

54
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:10,960
You can't even handle an imposter!

55
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:11,439
Boss!

56
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,120
Boss, I was wrong!

57
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:13,319
What's the use of having you!

58
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:14,280
Boss, I was wrong!

59
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,479
I was wrong, boss!

60
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,040
I was wrong!

61
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:16,879
Second Young Master!

62
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,279
Time to pay up!

63
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,680
Didn't I ask for a few more days?

64
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:25,959
It's not like I can't pay you back.

65
00:04:26,759 --> 00:04:27,680
He Jinchuan!

66
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:30,040
If it weren't for the He family's name,

67
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,680
we wouldn't have let you keep stalling.

68
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,199
Do you think we are pushovers?

69
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:36,279
Get him!

70
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,040
I'll pay! I'll pay!

71
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:46,879
I'll pay!

72
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:48,920
I was wrong!

73
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,199
I...

74
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,360
I'll pay!

75
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:52,439
Alright.

76
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,519
Listen up,

77
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:55,959
I have video evidence this time.

78
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,279
One more week.

79
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,839
If you still don't pay by then,

80
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,240
I will go to your father.

81
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:03,560
Please don't tell my father!

82
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:04,600
I'll pay!

83
00:05:05,199 --> 00:05:05,959
I'll definitely pay!

84
00:05:08,079 --> 00:05:08,480
Let's go.

85
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:23,560
For goodness' sake!

86
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:34,519
Boss,

87
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,720
I have taken care of him.

88
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:36,839
Are you satisfied?

89
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,680
Please don't tell my father!

90
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:41,800
I'll pay!

91
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:43,199
I'll definitely pay!

92
00:05:43,279 --> 00:05:45,000
When boss saw Miss Su's injured face,

93
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,399
he was really heartbroken.

94
00:05:46,839 --> 00:05:49,839
Not killing him was mercy enough.

95
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,800
That trash He Jinchuan

96
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,439
dares to touch my woman.

97
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,720
He deserves a lesson.

98
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,519
I did not expect

99
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,279
that you have this hobby.

100
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,920
Why brings you here?

101
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,040
Boss,

102
00:06:17,839 --> 00:06:19,519
Miss Su could not reach you by phone,

103
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,199
so she asked me.

104
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,199
Then I told her.

105
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:23,160
You two can keep practicing.

106
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,319
We will take off.

107
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,040
Let's go.

108
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,040
Care to spar?

109
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,519
Anytime.

110
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,319
You beat up He Jinchuan for me?

111
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:56,360
Whether it's an open attack
or a hidden arrow,

112
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,560
I will take it for you.

113
00:06:59,079 --> 00:07:00,000
But the ones who shoot those arrows

114
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,120
will pay the full price.

115
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,720
Do you really like me?

116
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,519
Why?

117
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,000
Trying to force a confession out of me?

118
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:22,439
It is more than like.

119
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,000
It is love.

120
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,759
Why? I can't kiss you?

121
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:37,120
My man

122
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,920
is mine to kiss.

123
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:10,079
Can you not go back?

124
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,199
I have to.

125
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:15,360
It's not time to confront He Jinchen.

126
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:21,480
You don't have to
fake Gu Qingmei anymore.

127
00:08:22,439 --> 00:08:23,000
And

128
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:26,439
we have already entered
Meiyan's board of directors

129
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:27,560
and planted our people inside.

130
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:29,800
Finding leverage against He Jinchen

131
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,680
is only a matter of time.

132
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,039
But right now,

133
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,960
the He family is targeting the resort.

134
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,360
I cannot just stand by.

135
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:38,360
Besides,

136
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,399
that trash He Jinchuan

137
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,000
needs a real lesson.

138
00:08:44,759 --> 00:08:45,679
Otherwise, I can't even enjoy my food.

139
00:08:48,039 --> 00:08:48,960
Then stay safe.

140
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,200
Alright.

141
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:01,240
I'm off.

142
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,279
Bye.

143
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:23,879
(Boss, we found something.)

144
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:26,080
(The thugs at Yunhu Resort)

145
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,799
(were sent by Second Young Master.)

146
00:09:29,159 --> 00:09:30,240
(He Jinchuan?)

147
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,120
(Why did he do that?)

148
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:32,919
(It is said)

149
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:35,120
(he made a promise to your father.)

150
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,879
(If he helps Shengda)

151
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,759
(complete the resort acquisition,)

152
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:41,120
(Mr. He would consider putting
Meiyan International)

153
00:09:41,279 --> 00:09:42,200
(in his charge.)

154
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,639
(Keep digging)

155
00:09:47,879 --> 00:09:49,879
(into everything reckless
He Jinchuan has done.)

156
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:53,080
(Don't miss a single detail,
no matter how small.)

157
00:09:53,399 --> 00:09:53,799
(Understood.)

158
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:57,559
He Jinchuan.

159
00:09:58,559 --> 00:10:01,559
I never expected you
to have such ambitions.

160
00:10:58,039 --> 00:10:58,840
What are you looking for?

161
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,960
I never expected you

162
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:09,039
to have a habit of reading
your wife's diary.

163
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:13,559
I just wanted to get to know you better.

164
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,480
To know me better?

165
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:17,200
We have been married for five years.

166
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:18,960
Isn't it too late for that?

167
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:20,960
Qingmei,

168
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,480
about this...

169
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,200
Enough. Here.

170
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,559
Take it and get to know me.

171
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:26,720
I'm a person

172
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,039
with no secrets.

173
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:42,960
Thank goodness, I'm smart.

174
00:11:56,279 --> 00:11:57,080
What's wrong, Niannian?

175
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,039
He Jinchuan!

176
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,759
Look at this!

177
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,960
This...

178
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:04,600
You've been cheating on me!

179
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,360
Let me explain!

180
00:12:05,519 --> 00:12:06,720
This video is fake!

181
00:12:07,799 --> 00:12:09,039
I would recognize you anywhere.

182
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,200
That's not true, Niannian.

183
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,320
Let me explain!

184
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,480
This video is fake!

185
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:15,440
I can't believe it.

186
00:12:15,679 --> 00:12:17,399
Money really does change men.

187
00:12:17,879 --> 00:12:19,679
Even a rich heir like you, Jinchuan?

188
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:21,759
Didn't your investment make money?

189
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:24,080
Did you spend it all on other women?

190
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,120
You trash!

191
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:27,159
You've been sneaking around
with other women!

192
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:27,639
I want my money back!

193
00:12:27,639 --> 00:12:28,720
- Niannian, calm down!
- I want a divorce.!

194
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:30,200
Niannian, I can explain it!

195
00:12:30,639 --> 00:12:31,080
Niannian!

196
00:12:31,159 --> 00:12:31,720
Get away from me!

197
00:12:31,799 --> 00:12:33,120
Let me explain, Niannian!

198
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,279
Why do you destroy

199
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:37,080
Jinchuan and Niannian's marriage?

200
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:39,200
When did you become so scheming?

201
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,320
What's wrong with that?

202
00:12:41,399 --> 00:12:43,360
Ever since I lowered my standards,

203
00:12:43,559 --> 00:12:45,120
I have never felt better.

204
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:45,720
You...

205
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,919
Are you still that Gu Qingmei I know?

206
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:52,919
I don't even remember myself.

207
00:12:53,559 --> 00:12:54,600
You remember that clearly?

208
00:12:55,799 --> 00:12:56,639
But...

209
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:59,279
I have forgotten many things,

210
00:12:59,679 --> 00:13:00,399
but

211
00:13:00,879 --> 00:13:01,960
I hold grudges.

212
00:13:03,799 --> 00:13:05,399
You sent that video?

213
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,200
Yes.

214
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:09,080
Friend or foe,

215
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:10,480
a video tells you everything.

216
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:13,480
Xu Niannian has the right
to know the truth.

217
00:13:20,879 --> 00:13:22,679
(You're not Gu Qingmei anymore.)

218
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,679
(Who are you?)

219
00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:45,820
(In control)

220
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:50,140
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

221
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:54,980
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

222
00:13:54,980 --> 00:13:59,540
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

223
00:13:59,540 --> 00:14:04,460
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

224
00:14:04,460 --> 00:14:08,260
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

225
00:14:08,260 --> 00:14:13,060
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

226
00:14:13,060 --> 00:14:15,900
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

227
00:14:15,900 --> 00:14:18,580
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

228
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:24,500
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

229
00:14:24,900 --> 00:14:31,700
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

230
00:14:31,980 --> 00:14:36,660
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

231
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:43,620
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

232
00:14:43,940 --> 00:14:50,740
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

233
00:14:50,940 --> 00:14:55,420
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

234
00:14:55,420 --> 00:14:58,780
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

235
00:14:58,780 --> 00:15:05,700
♪Right as I confess my love♪
